"Based on Atari's Warlords (1980) — castle defense meets Breakout in a head-"
"to-head duel."
msgstr "بناءاً على أمراء (آتاري) (1980)..."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw.html.heex:76
